```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Client [Client-Side]
        A[Web Browser / Mobile]
    end

    subgraph CDN [Frontend Hosting: Vercel / Netlify]
        B[Static Assets HTML/CSS/JS]
        C[Public Audit Dashboard]
    end

    subgraph Backend [Backend Hosting: Render / Railway]
        D[Node.js Express App]
        E[Auth Middleware DBAC/RBAC]
        F[Controllers & Routes]
    end

    subgraph Persistence [Database & Storage]
        G[(PostgreSQL DB on Supabase/Render)]
        H[Cloudinary Media Storage]
    end

    A -->|HTTPS Requests| B
    A -->|HTTPS Requests| C
    B -->|REST API / JSON| D
    C -->|Unauthenticated REST API| D
    
    D --> E
    E --> F
    F -->|SQL Queries| G
    F -->|Uploads| H
```
